thread.title: ALEJANDRO
thread.title_full: Redspot Car Rentals reviewed by ALEJANDRO

author: ALEJANDRO
title: ALEJANDRO
text:
Friendly staff at Melbourne Airport counter.
Car already prepared with the additional items requested in reservation (GPS device, child seat).
Car in perfect conditions which drove me thru Australia without any problem.
Easy and very quick return at Brisbane Airport.
I received final invoice via e-mail matching exactly with pre-arranged rental costs.
